default5)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultTo prevent breaches, most lib
defaultrary services subscribe to an internet filtering service, which is configured to prevent access to sites falling into a range of categories.  
defaultIn Norfolk, this is the same product that is used for filtering staff internet access, so any product must be capa
defaultble of handling more than one filtering regime profile.
default&#xa0;
default6)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultWe use the same filtering product for our public 
defaultwifi
default access in libraries as we do on static computers, although we believe this is by no means a common feature in other library authorities
default&#xa0;
default7)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultDifferen
defaultt filtering products 
defaultcategorise
default sites differently, so application of a national standard will be difficult – filtering service providers regard their classification methodologies as commercially confidential
default&#xa0;
default8)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultFiltering is applied at the site level, not at 
defaultthe content level.  It is therefore not currently possible to block adult video content on YouTube
default without blocking all video content.
default&#xa0;
default9)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultYouTube is the default hosting service for all Norfolk County Council public video content, so any idea of a national bl
defaultock on providing access to YouTube in libraries would have significant impact on the delivery and distribution of information about council services. 
default&#xa0;
default10)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultNorfolk Library and Information Services would like to see all websites that do or may host adult 
defaultmaterial to be required to hold it in an easily identifiable section of their site, so filtering software rules can be applied
default&#xa0;
defaultNorfolk Library and Information Service do not currently 
defaultmake any distinction about what a customer can access, within the bound
defaults of our acceptable use policy, based on age.
default&#xa0;
defaultThis is largely because there is no national standard about what is and isn’t acceptable within each age range, or even what those age ranges should be
default&#xa0;
defaultOur current age categories for borrowing books are:
default&#xa0;
defaultUnd
defaulter 5
default5 – 11
default12 - 15
default16 – 18
defaultOver 18
default&#xa0;
default11)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultNorfolk Library and Information Service do
defaultes
default not view it as the responsibility of a local library service to determine what is acceptable at each age, nor do we have the resources to do so – that should be set nationally and applied consistently across all filtering services so no local variation is
default possible.
default&#xa0;
default12)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultNorfolk Library and Information Service 
defaultdoes
default currently view it as the responsibility of the parent or guardian to monitor and control the internet activity of their children while they are on library premises.  Our safeguarding policy states th
defaultat no children under the age of 8 should be in a library unaccompanied.
default&#xa0;
default13)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultHaving said that, use of computers in libraries in Norfolk by children and young people is not that high, according to our usage statistics.  
defaultHowever, as more free public 
defaultwifi
default is roll
defaulted out across Norfolk, we may find the proportion of children accessing the internet across our 
defaultwifi
default network (and hence our filtering regime) but on their own devices increases.
default&#xa0;
default14)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAccess to social media sites is one of the most popular uses of uses of 
defaultpublic computers and is used by customers to keep in touch with their friends and family across the world.  Any recommendation to filter out use of social media sites in public libraries would have a severe impact on the positive benefits of social network
defaulting for library customers.
default For this reason we would be opposed to the principle of blocking internet access to social media sites in libraries. 
default&#xa0;
default15)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultManagement of a filtered internet service requires resources
default and a degree of technical expertise to provide it.  This is a skill set that will probably be unavailable to most groups who may wish to take over the running of a local library service on a voluntary basis.
default&#xa0;
defaultThere should therefore be a commitment that 
defaultthe local authority will make sufficient funding available to continue to provide a comprehensive and secure IT infrastructure in volunteer run libraries.  This will also help to support the Government’s Digital by Default policy
default&#xa0;
